{{version030}}
{{flavour|Splits the earth to draw up a localized, short-lived volcano under the target.}}

'''Eruption''' is a monster-only spell which deals 50% irresistible [[fire]] damage and creates temporary [[lava]] around the target (pushing items in the way). Lava from this spell can be used to cast [[Pyroclastic Surge]]. The lava creation works identically as [[Upheaval]] - each empty tile around you has a chance to become a lava tile.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.30]], Eruption was 45% irresistible (45% physical, 55% fire).
*Eruption was added in [[0.28]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
